<L>__{interior ben's kitchen afternoon}
<A>__{... stanley erupts into the kitchen like a great black bull in white suit and white shoes. a scarlet tie is matched by a huge handkerchief hanging from his pocket. he is a little drunk.}
<C>__{stanley}
<P>__{(obviously surprised}
<D>__{by this family}
<P>__{scene)}
<D>__{oh!}
<P>__{(then grinning and laughing thunderously)}
<D>__{merry christmas, everyone!}
